links = {'authorization_endpoint': {'url': 'http://link_endpoint'}}
rel_content = BeautifulSoup('<link rel="authorization_endpoint" href="foo">',
    'html.parser')
abs_content = BeautifulSoup(
    '<link rel="authorization_endpoint" href="http://foo/">', 'html.parser')
assert indieauth.find_endpoint('http://example', links=links
    ) == 'http://link_endpoint'
assert indieauth.find_endpoint('http://example', content=rel_content
    ) == 'http://example/foo'
assert indieauth.find_endpoint('http://example', content=abs_content
    ) == 'http://foo/'
assert indieauth.find_endpoint('http://example', links=links, content=
    rel_content) == 'http://link_endpoint'
assert not requests_mock.called
